{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"b0582fc2-7dd7-4f29-a291-bac76ca02f11","content":"","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"tooluse_nYp7m9Qd66lmr6ZP86NJzc","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Providing crash dump config"},"type":"function"}],"interactionId":"53eadead-7b45-4a9b-bbe0-80ea80c0e173","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user wants to configure automatic crash dump collection for a NativeAOT .NET 11 app running in Kubernetes. They have `createdump` installed at `/opt/tools/createdump`. Let me provide the necessary configuration.\n\nFor .NET NativeAOT apps, crash dump collection works differently than regular CoreCLR apps. The key environment variables are:\n\n1. `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump` - enables automatic dump collection on crash\n2. `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType` - sets the dump type (1=Normal, 2=WithHeap, 3=Triage, 4=Full)\n\n\n3. `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName` - specifies where to save the dump file\n4. `DOTNET_CreateDumpDiagnostics` - enables diagnostics output during dump creation\n5. `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath` - points to the createdump executable when it's not in the standard location\n\nFor NativeAOT in .NET 7+, I need to verify the exact variable names since the runtime handles this differently than standard CoreCLR.\n\nActually, with NativeAOT in .NET 8 and later, crash dump support relies on the `createdump` tool, but since NativeAOT doesn't bundle the runtime, I need to explicitly configure the path using `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath` to point to where createdump is located.\n\nFor the environment variables, `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump=1` turns on mini dumps, `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType` controls what gets captured, and `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName` specifies where the dumps are written. In Kubernetes, I'll need to handle storage with an emptyDir or persistent volume, ensure the `SYS_PTRACE` capability is granted so createdump can attach to processes, and potentially enable `shareProcessNamespace` depending on the setup. Let me put together a complete pod configuration that covers all this.","outputTokens":704,"requestId":"C3D7:31353F:1C9D8B6:203918C:6A07C20F"},"id":"918bfcc9-6e6d-4740-a6c2-aa5737b50a25","timestamp":"2026-05-16T01:02:21.676Z","parentId":"05f83854-35d2-43f8-9b2f-2b812581768a"}
